A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Criminal Procedure – Theft – Notification of Victims and Victims’
3 Representatives
4 FOR the purpose of requiring a prosecuting attorney of certain thefts to notify the victim
5 or the victim’s representative about certain information related to court proceedings;
6 and generally relating to notification to victims and victims’ representatives.
